Don’t know if anyone clarified it yet, but Toad isn’t wearing a hat. It was confirmed by Nintendo that it was part of his head. 

There was an UNOFFICIAL Super Mario Bros show made a while ago, that first made the thing of Toad having a hat. 

But it was also confirmed by Nintendo that the show wasn’t canon. Also Toad is a mushroom, so it would be part of his head. 

So in conclusion, it is most definitely a part of his head. You can’t take it off (or at least, not including cutting it off).
